1. *Usne* su najlepši deo tela neke osobe. (The lips are the most beautiful part of someone's body.)

2. Ona je imala veoma upečatljive *usne*. (She had very striking lips.)

3. On je poljubio svoju devojku u *usne*. (He kissed his girlfriend on the lips.)

4. Ona je pravila grimase i pokazivala svoje *usne*. (She was making faces and showing her lips.)

5. Naše *usne* su se spojile u poljubac. (Our lips met in a kiss.)

6. On je ljubio svoje dete po *usnama*. (He kissed his child on the lips.)